 Justification:
 Basis for FY2027 budget request is to continue to fund the F-35B total active inventory of 210 aircraft, with an inventory objective of 272. FY2027 funding increased primarily to accelerate Block 4 kit
 procurements and increase the pace of installations as depot capacity grows to avoid aircraft grounding due to life limits. F-35B TR-3 requirement was extended. Due to the update in requirements, additional
 TR-3 kit purchases are seen in FY2027 as well as additional DMS DTIP (Digital Tuner Insertion Program) hardware in FY2027. DMS DTIP parts are a prerequisite for the installation of TR-3 on non-DTIP
 Production aircraft (pre-Lot 12).




